{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:04:09.120294+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 80c6ad3f2330912d8cfabf6943b33205b9c5e93c)", "id": "lc_4c7f0f20-4b19-4266-8e93-1f4e778a2c12"}, {"type": "text", "text": "import { defineConfig } from 'vite';\nimport react  from '@vitejs/plugin-react';\nimport * as path from 'path';\nimport { existsSync } from 'fs';\nimport * as dotenv from 'dotenv';\n\n// Dotenv 是一个零依赖的模块，它能将环境变量中的变量从 .env 文件加载到 process.env 中\ndotenv.config({\n    path: existsSync('.env') ? '.env' : path.resolve('envs', `.env.${process.env.NODE_ENV}`)\n});\n\n// https://vitejs.dev/config/\nexport default defineConfig({\n    plugins: [react()],\n    resolve: {\n        alias: {\n            '@@': path.resolve(__dirname),\n            '@': path.resolve(__dirname, 'src')\n        }\n    },\n    server: {\n        cors: true,\n        port: process.env.VITE_PORT as unknown as number,\n        hmr: {\n            host: 'localhost',\n            protocol: 'ws',\n            port: process.env.VITE_PORT as unknown as number\n        }\n    }\n});\n", "id": "lc_a2ca3c2b-05a4-4dc8-b945-ed9905dc415b"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "23e2d072-feec-45cb-8109-65e0ad92af90", "tool_call_id": "call_01_ZFazf92EPjK4ycJUHWFE9253", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:04:09.122428+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: d358adc7f0dcdfe6e7b8db61c4c2e98880162b1c)", "id": "lc_8eea46ec-e15b-415e-b252-bf2905d5572d"}, {"type": "text", "text": "FROM node:lts-alpine as builder\n\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY . .\nRUN yarn\nRUN yarn build\n\nFROM nginx:alpine\nCOPY --from=builder /app/dist /usr/share/nginx/html\nCOPY --from=builder /app/nginx.conf /etc/nginx/conf.d/default.conf\n\n# 设置 nginx 作为默认命令启动\nCMD [\"nginx\", \"-g\", \"daemon off;\"]\n\n# 设置端口\nEXPOSE 80", "id": "lc_9a0eb3e7-0ec6-4088-9a58-ec514606129e"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "9ffc1055-3a90-45f1-b334-e39eb123b121", "tool_call_id": "call_00_D9HTGjTbT45UhAPEqicB7130", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:04:18.211784+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "## Findings\n\n### Package Manager: **Yarn**\n\nThe repository uses **Yarn** as its package manager. This is evidenced by:\n\n- **`yarn.lock`** – a lockfile present in the root of the repository (the `yarn.lock` blob is committed).\n- **`package.json` scripts** – the `fix` script runs `yarn lint --fix`.\n- **`Taskfile.yaml`** – the `init` task runs `yarn install`, and the `release` task runs `yarn release`.\n- **`Dockerfile`** – uses `RUN yarn` and `RUN yarn build` to install dependencies and build the project.\n\nAlthough `npm` commands appear in the Taskfile (for global CLI tool installations), the **primary/expected package manager for contributors is Yarn**.\n\n---\n\n### Environment-Specific npm Scripts (`package.json`)\n\n| Script | Purpose | Environment |\n|---|---|---|\n| `dev` | Start local dev server (`vite --host`) | `local` (via `cross-env NODE_ENV=local`) |\n| `dev:stg` | Start dev server for staging | `stg` (via `cross-env NODE_ENV=stg`) |\n| `serve` | Preview the built application (`vite preview --host`) | – |\n| `build` | Build for production (`vite build --mode prod`) | `prod` (default) |\n| `build:stg` | Build for staging (`vite build --mode test`) | `test` (via `cross-env`) |\n| `build:prod` | Explicit production build (`vite build --mode production`) | `production` |\n| `deploy` | Deploy the `dist` folder to GitHub Pages via `gh-pages -d dist` | – |\n| `lint` | Run ESLint on `.jsx/.js/.ts/.tsx` files | – |\n| `fix` | Auto-fix lint errors (`yarn lint --fix`) | – |\n\n---\n\n### Environment-Specific Configuration Files (`envs/`)\n\n| File | Environment |\n|---|---|\n| `envs/.env.local` | Local development |\n| `envs/.env.stg` | Staging |\n| `envs/.env.prod` | Production |\n\nThe **`vite.config.ts`** loads the appropriate `.env` file by checking for a `.env` file at the root, or falling back to `envs/.env.<NODE_ENV>` based on the `NODE_ENV` environment variable.\n\n---\n\n### Taskfile Scripts (for Development Workflow)\n\n| Task | Description |\n|---|---|\n| `task init` | Install global tools (`conventional-changelog-cli`, `standard-version`, `commitizen`), copy `envs/.env.local` → `.env`, and run `yarn install` |\n| `task changelog` | Generate a changelog via `conventional-changelog` |\n| `task release` | Fetch, run `yarn release`, generate changelog, stage files, and commit via `git cz` |\n| `task commit` | Stage all changes, commit via `git cz`, and push |", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 933, "prompt_tokens": 7410, "total_tokens": 8343, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 252, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 6912}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 6912, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 498}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-flash", "system_fingerprint": "fp_8b330d02d0_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "48a24607-ceaa-45e5-97ed-e28d8242d2de", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3e6-71a3-7be0-89c8-0abfc06e161e-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 7410, "output_tokens": 933, "total_tokens": 8343, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 6912}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 252}}}}]}}}
